c: 12
v: 38
t: "Apne buzurgon, Ibrahim, Ishaq aur yaqub ka tareeqa ikhtiyar kiya hai, hamara yeh kaam nahin hai ke Allah ke saath kisi ko shareek tehehrayein .Dar-haqeeqat yeh Allah ka fazal hai humpar aur Insaano par (ke usne apne siwa kisi ka banda humein nahin banaya) magar aksar log shukar nahin karte"